00:00:02,560 --> 00:00:05,640
Hello. Ladybug and Cat Noir saved Paris

00:00:05,640 --> 00:00:08,280
once again. Jand Park was recently

00:00:08,280 --> 00:00:09,920
turned into a terrifying magician under a spell

00:00:09,920 --> 00:00:12,440
and was about to destroy the Eiffel Tower

00:00:12,440 --> 00:00:15,280
in a cloud of smoke.

00:00:26,199 --> 00:00:30,320
Oh dear, you don't look well. Take me to the doctor,

00:00:30,320 --> 00:00:34,000
Marinette. But Tikki, where am I going to find

00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:36,879
a doctor? I know someone. I'll tell you where to go,

00:00:36,879 --> 00:00:39,160
but what will I say? You're a secret,

00:00:39,160 --> 00:00:41,640
he'll get suspicious if he sees you and ask questions.

00:00:41,640 --> 00:00:44,920
Besides, there's someone else who'll ask a lot of questions:

00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:48,280
my teacher. I'm late again. Tikki,

00:00:48,280 --> 00:00:52,160
shall I take you after school? What do

00:00:52,480 --> 00:00:56,399
you say? Thank you. Internal combustion

00:00:56,399 --> 00:00:58,800
is the exothermic chemical reaction of fuel

00:00:58,800 --> 00:01:01,760
and oxidizer, reaching high temperatures,

00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:04,159
at atmospheric pressure. Today, Prince Ali,

00:01:04,159 --> 00:01:06,840
heir to the throne of the Kingdom of Achu,

00:01:06,840 --> 00:01:08,920
is making a trip to Paris to launch

00:01:08,920 --> 00:01:10,920
a toy donation campaign for sick children

00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:13,439
at Paris City Hospital. How

00:01:13,439 --> 00:01:17,159
handsome he is, and his heart is as good as gold.

00:01:17,159 --> 00:01:19,600
Look, I want to write him a letter

00:01:19,600 --> 00:01:22,880
expressing my admiration and respect for him.

00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:26,479
Ah, Marinette. What's your excuse this time?

00:01:26,479 --> 00:01:28,840
Did you get accidentally locked in the bathroom again?

00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:31,479
Of course not. No, I had to take my, um,

00:01:31,479 --> 00:01:34,399
dog to the doctor because he ate my sweater.

00:01:34,399 --> 00:01:37,040
Oh, he could get very sick. Thank you, Rose.

00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:39,560
But I don't think our class needs any more odor.

00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:41,240
I thought someone brought a fish sandwich,

00:01:41,240 --> 00:01:44,240
but actually it's just Rose's perfume.

00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:55,520
Using a cell phone inside is forbidden.

00:01:55,520 --> 00:01:58,240
Collect your remaining belongings and go

00:01:58,240 --> 00:02:01,840
to the principal's office immediately.

00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:09,080
Did you see that? That's what happens

00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:12,959
when you play with flammable substances in the chemistry lab.

00:02:17,160 --> 00:02:19,840
And don't forget that tomorrow

00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:23,530
I will test you on laboratory safety.

00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:31,599
Dude, you're like twins. Neither of you can

00:02:31,599 --> 00:02:33,720
make it to school on time. Since Adrien

00:02:33,720 --> 00:02:35,360
missed chemistry class, wouldn't it be nice

00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:37,319
if someone gave him the notes he couldn't take?

00:02:37,319 --> 00:02:40,599
You're right. So, should I give him the notes?

00:02:44,879 --> 00:02:48,480
Uh, no, I can't. I, uh... Sweetie, I'm definitely

00:02:48,480 --> 00:02:51,560
not buying these excuses.

00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:56,640
I think I'm getting sick. Then talk

00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:02,800
less. I don't feel well at all. Don't worry,

00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:05,000
Tikki, it won't take long.

00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:11,879
Hey, are you okay? Is something wrong? Uh, yes. I'm

00:03:11,879 --> 00:03:14,120
fine.

00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:22,680
Adrien. Sabrina, what is Prince Ali doing today?

00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:26,280
They said he's giving out toys to children. Huh.

00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:30,100
I guess this is a plush toy. Whose could it be?

00:03:32,519 --> 00:03:35,360
The Prince has never seen anything like it, and

00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:37,480
when he sees me, Prince Ali will have forgotten

00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:40,640
all about the sick children.

00:03:40,640 --> 00:03:44,840
Did you say Prince Ali, or did you just mean

00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:47,480
him? None of your business. The Prince's father's

00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:50,239
hotel is the only hotel fit for princes,

00:03:50,239 --> 00:03:53,400
and I will be the first to meet him. How lucky.

00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:55,640
But please, could you give him this letter from me?

00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:57,439
Of course.

00:03:57,439 --> 00:04:00,680
How thoughtful of you to do this.

00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:02,480
Did you really believe that?

00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:06,319
Do you think I would take this smelly thing with me?

00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:25,720
Tikki! Ah, Chloé, wait, that's mine. Not

00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:31,360
anymore. It's mine now.

00:04:58,840 --> 00:05:01,479
Whenever I see a broken-hearted princess, I know

00:05:01,479 --> 00:05:02,560
her well.

00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:07,240
Every rose has its thorn.

00:05:14,479 --> 00:05:16,220
Fly, my little akuma, and evilize her.

00:05:29,759 --> 00:05:33,600
Dear princess, I am Hawk Moth. From now on, your secret

00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:37,440
weapon will be your perfume. No one will be able to resist it,

00:05:37,440 --> 00:05:40,360
especially Prince Ali. All I ask in return

00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:42,880
is that you bring me Ladybug and

00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:46,120
Cat Noir's Miraculous. I'm coming,

00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:48,420
my prince.

00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,880
Hello, I'm from Chloé Bourgeois'

00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:07,120
class and I must see her. Are you

00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:11,120
her friend? Am I her friend? You must be joking.

00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:13,639
I mean, we're just in the same class, that's all. If you're not

00:06:13,639 --> 00:06:16,599
her friend, you can't come in. Yes, I am

00:06:16,599 --> 00:06:17,800
Chloé's friend.

00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:20,360
We're very close.

00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:23,080
Chloé doesn't have any friends. So,

00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:28,150
are you not going to let me in? No.

00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:43,630
He usually eats sushi. The top floor Royal

00:06:58,520 --> 00:07:02,120
Suite, you mean? Prince... Ah, it's not important.

00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:04,599
You're spoiling me, really.

00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:10,720
No, no. That's better.

00:07:14,919 --> 00:07:18,319
Ha, pizza? Ugh, don't bring that poor people's food

00:07:18,319 --> 00:07:20,879
any closer.

00:07:28,520 --> 00:07:32,520
I've come to see Prince Ali. Ah,

00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:35,360
what's going on today? Do you have a date with the Prince?

00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:37,800
No need. I am a princess myself.

00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:40,160
I am a princess. Listen, kid.

00:07:40,160 --> 00:07:43,919
You don't speak to a princess like that.

00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:48,360
At your service, Princess Fragrance. That's much

00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:50,599
better. Now, where is my handsome prince?

00:07:50,599 --> 00:07:54,039
I shouldn't keep him waiting.

00:07:56,280 --> 00:08:00,360
In honor of your visit to Paris, I have personally arranged

00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:02,319
a fireworks display over the Seine River

00:08:02,319 --> 00:08:04,319
just for you.

00:08:04,319 --> 00:08:06,440
The fireworks will be launched from this boat.

00:08:06,440 --> 00:08:09,930
Thank you. How do you say it in your language?

00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:17,080
This is wonderful. First, it must fit

00:08:17,080 --> 00:08:18,759
into the Prince's busy schedule. There is very little time

00:08:18,759 --> 00:08:21,159
for fun. His Majesty is a responsible

00:08:21,159 --> 00:08:24,560
person.

00:08:26,159 --> 00:08:28,800
Ali, if you'll permit me, let me introduce you

00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:31,879
to my own princess.

00:08:35,719 --> 00:08:39,479
Chloé. Prince, I brought you a very special

00:08:39,479 --> 00:08:42,240
gift for the sick children.

00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:44,680
I've never seen anything like it.

00:08:44,680 --> 00:08:48,040
How kind of you. You're spoiling me, but

00:08:48,040 --> 00:08:50,360
it was a lovely thought of mine. Isn't that right?

00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:53,240
Yes. As I was saying, didn't you hear me?

00:09:07,880 --> 00:09:10,640
Nadja, don't be surprised. This is just the news.

00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:12,800
Prince Ali, what can you tell us about this official

00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:14,600
visit to Paris?

00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:17,800
It's wonderful to be here. Prince Ali, this, uh...

00:09:17,800 --> 00:09:23,480
Uh, where is that smell coming from? Ah, like rotten fish.

00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:26,760
It's not from me.

00:09:26,760 --> 00:09:31,079
But is it from me?

00:09:33,640 --> 00:09:36,880
We are at your service, dear princess. And who

00:09:36,880 --> 00:09:39,760
are you? I am Princess Fragrance, and I have come here

00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:44,640
for you. Very soon you will be my Prince Ali.

00:09:50,920 --> 00:09:55,000
Who is this now? Plagg, Plagg, let's go.

00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:57,760
Paris is in trouble. I haven't finished my meal.

00:09:57,760 --> 00:10:01,320
Plagg!

00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:20,760
Claws out! Quickly, this way!

00:10:29,640 --> 00:10:31,200
This place is extremely secure, our door

00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:34,279
is made of steel. What is this chaos here?

00:10:34,279 --> 00:10:37,440
There's not a single person following the schedule.

00:10:38,959 --> 00:10:41,519
What is this now?

00:10:48,880 --> 00:10:53,160
Run! You will come to the scent of my eternal love!

00:10:55,160 --> 00:11:01,240
Are you serious? Who are you?

00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:05,120
Mother of... I can't take it anymore. You can't be

00:11:05,120 --> 00:11:09,000
a superhero now. There are two of them.

00:11:09,519 --> 00:11:14,079
You cannot escape my scent!

00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:34,120
Seize them, dear princess!

00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:44,200
At your service! They're all bewitched. Quick,

00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:46,680
close the door! But isn't that your father?

00:11:46,680 --> 00:11:49,519
What do I care? Close it, I said!

00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:59,720
At your service, dear princess.

00:12:02,680 --> 00:12:05,120
Can we get some fresh air?

00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:09,920
Plagg, absolutely not. You cannot take it from me!

00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:21,480
Emergency evacuation! Everyone downstairs!

00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:25,399
This is too dangerous for the Prince.

00:12:25,639 --> 00:12:31,160
You're right. Safety first.

00:12:50,920 --> 00:12:53,720
Prince, can we measure the window? This fish

00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:57,519
smells bad even to me.

00:12:59,959 --> 00:13:02,279
We have nine minutes to get to the hospital.

00:13:02,279 --> 00:13:05,440
The Prince's schedule is very tight. What?

00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:07,680
We can't go to a hospital right now. We need to get

00:13:07,680 --> 00:13:10,279
Prince Ali out of Paris.

00:13:10,279 --> 00:13:15,079
How nice to see you. What a great honor.

00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:20,720
I will take you, and we will seal our love!

00:13:22,800 --> 00:13:28,120
Cat Noir's gone. Ladybug! Ha!

00:13:43,079 --> 00:13:43,240
I'll find him. Tikki?

00:13:43,519 --> 00:13:48,959
Tikki, I was so worried. Marinette, you're worse

00:13:48,959 --> 00:13:51,759
than I thought. We need to go to a doctor.

00:13:51,759 --> 00:13:54,360
We don't have any time. You have to transform.

00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:57,440
Forget about me.

00:13:57,440 --> 00:14:00,480
No. I won't make the same mistake again.

00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:01,920
We have to get you to a doctor.

00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:15,519
She'll get better soon, won't she?

00:14:15,519 --> 00:14:17,680
One who burns with impatience cannot drink

00:14:17,680 --> 00:14:21,120
hot milk. What does milk have to do with it?

00:14:21,120 --> 00:14:23,079
Silence, please.

00:14:23,079 --> 00:14:27,040
I'm checking the energy.

00:14:28,040 --> 00:14:30,639
You said a breed of cat? Is it really a cat?

00:14:30,639 --> 00:14:33,399
Yes, a rare hairless flying cat from the Kingdom of Achu.

00:14:33,399 --> 00:14:35,399
It was given to me as a gift

00:14:35,399 --> 00:14:37,160
when I won a dance competition

00:14:37,160 --> 00:14:39,000
during a childhood trip to the Kingdom of Achu.

00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:43,320
Oh, that was a long time ago. Yes,

00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:46,920
quite. It's done now. Your cat's health

00:14:46,920 --> 00:14:49,360
is restored.

00:14:52,959 --> 00:14:56,320
Ah, thank you! Thank you so much!

00:14:56,320 --> 00:14:59,680
You are a magician, sir. How did you do that?

00:14:59,680 --> 00:15:03,079
Secrets of ancient China.

00:15:03,079 --> 00:15:05,680
Like your secret.

00:15:07,040 --> 00:15:10,800
Tikki, I'm so, so sorry. You were very sick

00:15:10,800 --> 00:15:13,320
and I don't know what I'd do without you.

00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:16,519
You couldn't be Ladybug, for instance.

00:15:16,519 --> 00:15:18,720
I know. But I'm serious, Tikki, you're more

00:15:18,720 --> 00:15:20,560
to me than just a kwami.

00:15:20,560 --> 00:15:23,560
I know.

00:15:24,759 --> 00:15:27,320
The bridge goes that way. They must have gone there.

00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:29,440
While they're in the car,

00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:31,639
we must act quickly, no time to lose.

00:15:31,639 --> 00:15:35,170
Tikki, spots on!

00:15:59,120 --> 00:16:01,720
I can't wait for us to be together,

00:16:01,720 --> 00:16:05,470
my prince. Servants, the love lock!

00:16:07,319 --> 00:16:10,519
With this, our love will be eternal.

00:16:10,519 --> 00:16:15,120
Prince, I am entirely at your service,

00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:17,759
Princess. The love lock!

00:16:17,759 --> 00:16:23,959
Hold it right there, you stinky thing!

00:16:29,680 --> 00:16:32,920
Use Cat Noir to reach Ladybug.

00:16:32,920 --> 00:16:36,440
Servants, attack! And bring me her earrings!

00:16:58,959 --> 00:17:02,440
Stop it, Cat Noir. You are mine, Ladybug.

00:17:02,440 --> 00:17:05,519
Give me your Miraculous!

00:17:07,119 --> 00:17:10,199
Why make our love eternal when you could be taking over Paris?

00:17:20,679 --> 00:17:23,480
This can't be happening. I need to put an end to this

00:17:23,480 --> 00:17:26,000
before something happens to me too.

00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:28,000
See? That's what happens

00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:30,280
when you play with flammable substances

00:17:30,280 --> 00:17:32,559
in the chemistry lab!

00:17:40,880 --> 00:17:44,679
It didn't come.

00:17:47,280 --> 00:17:49,120
You missed!

00:17:57,840 --> 00:18:00,919
Yes, finally you dropped it!

00:18:00,919 --> 00:18:04,130
Give me your Miraculous! Cataclysm!

00:18:30,840 --> 00:18:33,760
I never liked this city. There are too many people

00:18:33,760 --> 00:18:36,120
after us. Let's go far away from here.

00:18:36,120 --> 00:18:39,120
Come on, my prince. Were you leaving for somewhere far away?

00:18:39,120 --> 00:18:40,760
But the party's just

00:18:40,760 --> 00:18:44,240
getting started. You've ruined everything.

00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:49,120
And I will ruin you! Lucky Charm!

00:18:51,320 --> 00:18:55,180
A balloon? What am I going to do with this?

00:18:59,440 --> 00:19:03,680
You can't escape now, Ladybug. Give up!

00:19:12,159 --> 00:19:15,900
No more evil-doing for you!

00:19:19,480 --> 00:19:23,400
Akuma, let go of the evil!

00:19:25,120 --> 00:19:27,159
That's it. Goodbye,

00:19:27,159 --> 00:19:29,400
little butterfly.

00:19:29,400 --> 00:19:33,679
Miraculous Ladybug!

00:19:35,559 --> 00:19:37,960
What am I doing here? Where is

00:19:37,960 --> 00:19:39,640
Ladybug?

00:19:39,640 --> 00:19:42,960
Our whole schedule is ruined. We'll be late

00:19:42,960 --> 00:19:46,520
for everything. But where is the Prince?

00:19:46,520 --> 00:19:49,600
Wait a minute. Where am I?

00:19:49,600 --> 00:19:53,990
How did I get here? Prince

00:19:57,640 --> 00:20:01,919
Ali, and who are you? Never mind, I'll leave you

00:20:01,919 --> 00:20:04,520
to chat with your fan for a bit.

00:20:04,520 --> 00:20:06,960
See you later. I know you help sick children

00:20:06,960 --> 00:20:08,320
around the world, and I have to say,

00:20:08,320 --> 00:20:10,120
you are the kindest person

00:20:10,120 --> 00:20:12,400
I have ever met in my life.

00:20:12,400 --> 00:20:14,679
Really? I think so.

00:20:14,679 --> 00:20:17,720
You are kind. Luckily, I'm fine too.

00:20:17,720 --> 00:20:19,400
Aren't I? Let's pick up where we left off.

00:20:19,400 --> 00:20:22,200
There's no need, Miss Rose.

00:20:22,200 --> 00:20:24,600
I need to go see the children at the hospital.

00:20:24,600 --> 00:20:26,600
Let's hurry a bit, or else

00:20:26,600 --> 00:20:31,010
my assistant will be lost. Goodbye.